#Remapping Advantage Pro From Scratch

1. Switch Keyboard Mode To Mac (hold down equals then press m)

##Remap the keys: (anytime you want to remap - hold Program then F12 - when finished remapping Program - F12 to finish)

1. Caps Locks To Command Key - [Right Control - CapsLock]
2. Control Key - [Right Windows Key - Right Control]
3. Alt - [LeftAlt - Delete]
